t-3 px-3 pr-[10px] relative scroll-visible"><div class="grow p-[var(--spacing-chatInputBox)] pt-0 overflow-hidden "><div id="message-renderer" role="log" aria-live="polite" aria-relevant="additions" aria-atomic="false" class="flex-grow w-full"><div data-scroll-anchor="false" data-role="user"><div class="flex flex-col items-end py-4 pl-8 w-full"><div class="flex flex-col items-end group/userChatBox relative"><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 px-4 pt-3 pb-2 !pt-0"></div><div class="px-4 py-3 bg-surface-subtle rounded-[12px_12px_2px_12px] min-w-[110px] max-w-full bg-surface-default relative false"><div class="max-h-[150px] overflow-hidden "><p class="text-[14px] leading-[150%] break-words whitespace-break-spaces wrap-anywhere">You are an expert UI/UX designer and senior frontend engineer.

Your task is to create a world-class, visually stunning, highly modern landing page for a fintech AI platform called "FundFlow AI".

This is NOT a basic website. It should feel like Stripe, Ramp, Brex, or Vercel-level design quality.

----------------------------------------

🎯 PRODUCT CONTEXT:

FundFlow AI is a real-time fraud detection and investigation platform for public sector banks.

Core highlights:
- AI-powered fraud detection using XGBoost (AUC 0.9666)
- 48 engineered ML features
- 6-layer composite risk engine
- Real-time transaction monitoring via WebSockets
- Graph-based fraud detection (network visualization)
- SHAP explainability for every fraud decision
- India Stack native (UPI, KYC, PMLA integration)
- Real-time alerts and investigation workflows

This is a deep-tech AI + fintech product, not a generic SaaS tool.

----------------------------------------

🎨 DESIGN STYLE:

- Ultra-modern fintech SaaS design
- Dark theme (primary) with glassmorphism + gradients
- Smooth animations and micro-interactions
- Clean typography (Inter / Geist / Satoshi)
- Inspired by:
  - Stripe
  - Vercel
  - Linear
  - Ramp
  - AI startups (Perplexity, OpenAI UI)

----------------------------------------

🧱 TECH STACK (MANDATORY):

- React (Vite)
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion (for animations)
- Three.js OR React Three Fiber (for background visuals)
- ShadCN UI (components)
- Lucide Icons

----------------------------------------

✨ VISUAL REQUIREMENTS:

1. Animated background:
   - Subtle particle network OR flowing graph lines (representing transaction network)
   - Slight parallax effect
   - Glow + gradient motion

2. Glassmorphism cards with blur effects

3. Smooth scroll-based animations:
   - fade-in
   - slide-up
   - staggered elements

4. Hover interactions:
   - glowing borders
   - subtle scale
   - animated gradients

----------------------------------------

📄 LANDING PAGE STRUCTURE:

1. HERO SECTION:
   - Headline: “Real-Time Fraud Detection for Modern Banking”
   - Subtext: Explain AI + real-time + explainability
   - CTA buttons:
        [Request Demo] [View Live Simulation]
   - Right side:
        Animated visualization (network graph or fraud detection UI mock)

----------------------------------------

2. TRUST / STATS BAR:
   - AUC: 0.9666
   - 48 ML Features
   - 6 Risk Layers
   - Real-time processing

----------------------------------------

3. FEATURES SECTION (GRID):

Each card should have icon + animation:

- AI Fraud Detection Engine
- 6-Layer Risk Scoring System
- Real-Time Transaction Monitoring
- Graph-Based Fraud Detection
- SHAP Explainability
- India Stack Integration

----------------------------------------

4. HOW IT WORKS (PIPELINE VISUAL):

Step-by-step flow:

Transaction → ML Scoring → Risk Engine → Graph Analysis → Alert Generation

Make this visually connected (lines/arrows animation)

----------------------------------------

5. INTERACTIVE DEMO SECTION:

Simulated UI panel showing:
- live transactions
- fraud alerts
- risk scores

Include animated counters / fake live feed

----------------------------------------

6. WHY FUNDFLOW AI:

- Built for Public Sector Banks
- Not a black-box AI (Explainable)
- Real-time + scalable
- Regulatory aligned

----------------------------------------

7. CTA SECTION:

“Detect fraud before it happens”

Buttons:
- Get Started
- Book Demo

----------------------------------------

8. FOOTER:

- Links
- Socials
- Minimal clean layout

----------------------------------------

⚡ CODE REQUIREMENTS:

- Clean, modular React components
- Proper folder structure
- Reusable UI components
- Fully responsive
- Smooth performance (no lag)

----------------------------------------

🚫 AVOID:

- Basic templates
- Bootstrap-style UI
- Static boring layout
- Overcrowded design

----------------------------------------

🎯 OUTPUT:

Generate full working React code (Vite + Tailwind setup)
Include all components in a single file or structured files.

Focus heavily on visuals, animations, and premium feel.

