st-decimal [&amp;_ul]:!pl-4 [&amp;_ol]:!pl-4"><ul>
<li>Added <code node="[object Object]">ThemeContext</code> with light/dark toggle, persisting preference to <code node="[object Object]">localStorage</code> and applying <code node="[object Object]">data-theme="light"</code> to the HTML root</li>
<li>Added sun/moon icon toggle button to the Header (desktop + mobile) using <code node="[object Object]">useTheme</code> hook</li>
<li>Updated Tailwind color tokens (<code node="[object Object]">bg-primary</code>, <code node="[object Object]">bg-secondary</code>, <code node="[object Object]">text-primary</code>, <code node="[object Object]">accent-cyan</code>, etc.) to use CSS variables, and defined a clean premium light theme palette under <code node="[object Object]">[data-theme="light"]</code> in <code node="[object Object]">tailwind.css</code></li>
