<li>Added staggered hero reveal: badge → headline → subtext → CTAs → trust row → mockup each animate in sequentially on mount with spring easing</li>
<li>Added scroll-driven parallax depth to all three sections — background blobs shift at different speeds (0.08×–0.18× scroll rate) creating layered depth</li>
<li>Enhanced FeaturesSection with per-card <code node="[object Object]">IntersectionObserver</code> stagger reveals (scale + translateY) and improved hover micro-interactions (icon rotate, bottom glow line); DemoSection header and panel fade-up on scroll with a breathing <code node="[object Object]">panelGlow</code> animation</li>
